Implemented the minimal source fix.

Changed:

- `packages/svelte/src/compiler/phases/3-transform/client/visitors/ConstTag.js`
- `packages/svelte/src/compiler/phases/3-transform/server/visitors/ConstTag.js`

What changed:

- `{@const b = $derived(expr)}` now transforms using `expr` directly as the const tag’s derived value.
- `{@const b = $derived.by(fn)}` now transforms using `fn` as the derived function.
- Server-side transform similarly strips the rune wrapper and evaluates `$derived.by` by calling the provided function.

